                  <decoDesc>
                     <summary>Very big building made of stone, it is lowered in the ground, has a locked door on the north side with a fence and steps leading down. It has a coped roof with a big square stone on top. Every one of the 4 corners is decorated with an `ear' and the 3 sides (SEW) have a carved wreath on each, with different motifs inside. E: a painter's palette; S: a book; W: a hammer and other tools.</summary>
